description: This Chainlink VRF common Gaston purrs with a rating of 33, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 33, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Stringalong for East, Nine Lives for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60331-47910-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [33 Votes, Common]
